name: The Survivor (2022 Edition)
description:
Right on the first day of 2022, before an appointment with a medical professional, Uncle carries his left hand to one of his favorite restaurants to celebrate, ordering a Fresh Large Fish Au Naturel.
The place looks a little broken, and someone swings by to take a nap next to him, but the flamingo still works there, so it’s all good. 

JPG | 1417 x 1890 px
